WEBVTT

1
00:00:13.256 --> 00:00:15.116
In the movie "Interstellar,"
在电影《星际穿越》中，

2
00:00:14.810 --> 00:00:18.421
we get an up-close look at a supermassive black hole.
我们得以近距离观察一个超级黑洞。

3
00:00:18.491 --> 00:00:20.634
Set against a backdrop of bright gas,
在明亮气体构成的背景下，

4
00:00:20.658 --> 00:00:22.776
the black hole's massive gravitational pull
黑洞的巨大引力

5
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.235
bends light into a ring.
将光线弯曲成环形。

6
00:00:24.259 --> 00:00:26.368
However, this isn't a real photograph,
但是，（电影中的）这一幕 并不是一张真正的照片，

7
00:00:26.392 --> 00:00:28.178
but a computer graphic rendering --
而是电脑合成的效果——

8
00:00:28.202 --> 00:00:31.592
an artistic interpretation of what a black hole might look like.
它只是一个对于黑洞 可能样子的艺术表现。

9
00:00:32.221 --> 00:00:33.387
A hundred years ago,
一百多年前，

10
00:00:33.411 --> 00:00:37.012
Albert Einstein first published his theory of general relativity.
阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦 第一次发表了广义相对论学说。

11
00:00:36.906 --> 00:00:38.339
In the years since then,
在之后的数年里，

12
00:00:38.499 --> 00:00:41.472
scientists have provided a lot of evidence in support of it.
科学家们又对此提供了许多佐证。

13
00:00:41.496 --> 00:00:44.580
But one thing predicted from this theory, black holes,
但相对论中所预测的一点，黑洞，

14
00:00:44.604 --> 00:00:46.954
still have not been directly observed.
却始终无法被直接观察到。

15
00:00:46.978 --> 00:00:50.184
Although we have some idea as to what a black hole might look like,
尽管我们大致知道一个黑洞 看起来应该是什么样，

16
00:00:49.868 --> 00:00:52.971
