the imaging algorithms I develop use our limited telescope data
我正在开发的图片算法， 是使用望远镜提供的有限数据

149
00:06:57.390 --> 00:07:01.712
to guide us to a picture that also looks like stuff in our universe.
来生成一张看起来像是 宇宙里的东西的图片。

